'''Crozo Industrial Products'''<ref name="Rising Storm" /> was the company that manufactured the [[2-MAL personal comlink]], a communications device commonly used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic]].<ref name="Rogue One Visual Guide" /> During the [[High Republic Era]], an [[ancient deep-space transmitter]] from the [[Jedi Archives]] which was to be displayed at the [[Valo Republic Fair]] was going to be loaned to Crozo for a communications showcase afterwards.<ref name="Rising Storm" />

